      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2016 BMW M3 finished in stunning Mineral Grey Metallic over a vibrant Sakhir Orange extended leather interior. This vehicle has been a dedicated weekend driver and clearly shows the pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though close inspection reveals minor rock chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014honest wear consistent with a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine environment; the leather bolsters are firm with only light entry wear on the driver's side, and all onboard technology, from the Harmon Kardon surround sound system to the heads-up display, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this M3 is robust and turn-key. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a fresh oil change and brake fluid flush completed just last month. The Michelin Pilot Sport tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide confident, sharp stopping power. Included with the sale are two keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive folder of maintenance receipts. This is an excellent opportunity for an enthusiast seeking a reliable, well-documented performance sedan that balances cosmetic integrity with mechanical readiness.",
